563411,120,121,72,92,1,108,14,"Yasmā pana bhaṅgānupassanāya eva vipassanā sikhaṃ pāpuṇāti, tasmā visesetvā idameva‘‘ vipassane ñāṇan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
563412,120,121,93,113,1,189,19,"Yasmā udayabbayānupassanāya ṭhitassa maggāmaggañāṇadassanaṃ uppajjati, tasmā tassā siddhāya taṃ siddhameva hotīti taṃ avatvāva bhaṅgānupassanāya eva vipassanāsikhaṃ ñāṇaṃ vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
563413,120,121,114,148,1,270,29,"Udayabbayānupassanāya suparidiṭṭhaudayabbayassa suparicchinnesu saṅkhāresu lahuṃ lahuṃ upaṭṭhahantesu ñāṇe tikkhe vahante udayaṃ pahāya bhaṅge eva sati santiṭṭhati, tassa‘‘ evaṃ uppajjitvā evaṃ nāma saṅkhārā bhijjantī’’ ti passato etasmiṃ ṭhāne bhaṅgānupassanāñāṇaṃ uppajjati. "
563414,120,122,2,16,1,141,10,8. Bhayatupaṭṭhāne {paññā}ti uppādapavattanimittaāyūhanāpaṭisandhīnaṃ bhayato upaṭṭhāne pīḷāyogato sappaṭibhayavasena gahaṇūpagamane paññāti attho. 
563415,120,122,17,25,1,69,6,"Bhayato upaṭṭhātīti bhayatupaṭṭhānaṃ ārammaṇaṃ , tasmiṃ bhayatupaṭṭhāne. "
563416,120,122,26,43,1,88,11,"Atha vā bhayato upatiṭṭhatīti bhayatupaṭṭhānaṃ, paññā, taṃ‘‘ bhayatupaṭṭhānan’’ ti vuttaṃ hoti. "
563417,120,123,2,6,1,33,4,Ādīnave ñāṇan ti bhummavacanameva.
563418,120,123,7,48,1,186,24,"‘‘ Yā ca bhayatupaṭṭhāne paññā, yañca ādīnave ñāṇaṃ, yā ca nibbidā, ime dhammā ekaṭṭhā, byañjanameva nānan’’ ti( paṭi. ma.1.227) vuttattā ekamiva vuccamānampi avatthābhedena muñcitukamyatādi viya tividhameva hoti. "
563419,120,123,49,60,1,119,11,Tasmā bhayatupaṭṭhānaādīnavānupassanāsu siddhāsu nibbidānupassanā siddhā hotīti katvā avuttāpi vuttāva hotīti veditabbā. 
563420,120,124,2,44,1,533,34,"Sabbasaṅkhārānaṃ bhaṅgārammaṇaṃ bhaṅgānupassanaṃ āsevantassa bhāventassa bahulīkarontassa tibhavacatuyonipañcagatisattaviññāṇaṭṭhitinavasattāvāsesu pabhedakā saṅkhārā sukhena jīvitukāmassa bhīrukapurisassa sīhabyagghadīpiacchataracchayakkharakkhasacaṇḍagoṇacaṇḍakukkurapabhinna- madacaṇḍahatthighoraāsivisaasanivicakkasusānaraṇabhūmijalitaaṅgārakāsuādayo viya mahābhayaṃ hutvā upaṭṭhahanti, tassa‘‘ atītā saṅkhārā niruddhā, paccuppannā nirujjhanti, anāgatāpi evameva nirujjhissantī’’ ti passato etasmiṃ ṭhāne bhayatupaṭṭhānaṃ ñāṇaṃ uppajjati. "
563421,120,124,45,160,1,944,98,"Tassa taṃ bhayatupaṭṭhānañāṇaṃ āsevantassa bhāventassa bahulīkarontassa sabbabhavayonigatiṭhitisattāvāsesu neva tāṇaṃ na leṇaṃ na gati na paṭisaraṇaṃ paññāyati, sabbabhavayonigatiṭhitinivāsagatesu saṅkhāresu ekasaṅkhārepi patthanā vā parāmāso vā na hoti, tayo bhavā vītaccitaṅgārapuṇṇā aṅgārakāsuyo viya, cattāro mahābhūtā ghoravisā āsivisā viya, pañcakkhandhā ukkhittāsikā vadhakā viya, cha ajjhattikāyatanāni suññagāmo viya, cha bāhirāyatanāni gāmaghātakacorā viya, sattaviññāṇaṭṭhitiyo nava ca sattāvāsā ekādasahi aggīhi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā viya ca, sabbe saṅkhārā gaṇḍabhūtā rogabhūtā sallabhūtā aghabhūtā ābādhabhūtā viya ca nirassādā nirasā mahāādīnavarāsibhūtā hutvā upaṭṭhahanti, sukhena jīvitukāmassa bhīrukapurisassa ramaṇīyākārasaṇṭhitampi savāḷakamiva vanagahanaṃ, sasaddūlā viya guhā, sagāharakkhasaṃ viya udakaṃ, samussitakhaggā viya paccatthikā, savisaṃ viya bhojanaṃ, sacoro viya maggo, ādittamiva agāraṃ, uyyuttasenā viya raṇabhūmi. "
563422,120,124,161,187,1,243,25,"Yathā hi so puriso etāni savāḷakavanagahanādīni āgamma bhīto saṃviggo lomahaṭṭhajāto samantato ādīnavameva passati, evameva so yogāvacaro bhaṅgānupassanāvasena sabbasaṅkhāresu bhayato upaṭṭhitesu samantato nirasaṃ nirassādaṃ ādīnavameva passati. "
563423,120,124,188,192,1,48,4,Tassevaṃ passato ādīnavānupassanāñāṇaṃ uppajjati. 
563424,120,125,2,14,1,145,11,So evaṃ sabbasaṅkhāre ādīnavato sampassanto sabbabhavayonigativiññāṇaṭṭhitisattāvāsagate sabhedake saṅkhāragate nibbindati ukkaṇṭhati nābhiramati. 
563425,120,125,15,42,1,304,24,"Seyyathāpi nāma cittakūṭapabbatapādābhirato suvaṇṇarājahaṃso asucimhi caṇḍālagāmadvāraāvāṭe nābhiramati, sattasu mahāsaresuyeva abhiramati, evameva ayaṃ yogīrājahaṃso suparidiṭṭhādīnave sabhedake saṅkhāragate nābhiramati, bhāvanārāmatāya pana bhāvanāratiyā samannāgatattā sattasu anupassanāsuyeva abhiramati. "
563426,120,125,43,66,1,194,19,"Yathā ca suvaṇṇapañjarepi pakkhitto sīho migarājā nābhiramati, tiyojanasahassavitthate pana himavanteyeva ramati, evamayampi yogīsīho tividhe sugatibhavepi nābhiramati, tīsu anupassanāsuyeva ramati. "
563427,120,125,67,112,1,295,27,"Yathā ca sabbaseto sattappatiṭṭho iddhimā vehāsaṅgamo chaddanto nāgarājā nagaramajjhe nābhiramati, himavati chaddantarahadeyeva ramati, evamayaṃ yogīvaravāraṇo sabbasmimpi saṅkhāragate nābhiramati,‘‘ anuppādo kheman’’ tiādinā( paṭi. ma.1.53) nayena niddiṭṭhe santipadeyeva ramati, tanninnatappoṇatappabbhāramānaso hoti. "
563428,120,125,113,118,1,52,5,Ettāvatā tassa nibbidānupassanāñāṇaṃ uppannaṃ hotīti. 
563429,120,126,2,19,1,149,13,"9. Muñcitukamyatāpaṭisaṅkhāsantiṭṭhanā paññā saṅkhārupekkhāsu ñāṇan ti muñcituṃ cajituṃ kāmeti icchatīti muñcitukāmo, muñcitukāmassa bhāvo muñcitukamyatā. "
563430,120,126,20,27,1,67,6,"Paṭisaṅkhāti upaparikkhatīti paṭisaṅkhā, paṭisaṅkhānaṃ vā paṭisaṅkhā. "
563431,120,126,28,35,1,67,6,"Santiṭṭhati ajjhupekkhatīti santiṭṭhanā, santiṭṭhanaṃ vā santiṭṭhanā. "
563432,120,126,36,44,1,87,8,Muñcitukamyatā ca sā paṭisaṅkhā ca santiṭṭhanā cāti muñcitukamyatāpaṭisaṅkhāsantiṭṭhanā. 
563433,120,126,45,52,1,84,7,Iti pubbabhāge nibbidāñāṇena nibbinnassa uppādādīni pariccajitukāmatā muñcitukamyatā. 
563434,120,126,53,58,1,59,5,Muñcanassa upāyakaraṇatthaṃ majjhe paṭisaṅkhānaṃ paṭisaṅkhā. 
563435,120,126,59,63,1,43,4,Muñcitvā avasāne ajjhupekkhanaṃ santiṭṭhanā. 
563436,120,126,64,109,1,322,31,"Evaṃ avatthābhedena tippakārā paññā saṅkhārānaṃ ajjhupekkhanāsu ñāṇaṃ, muñcitukamyatāpaṭisaṅkhāsantiṭṭhanāsaṅkhātānaṃ avatthābhedena bhinnānaṃ tissannampi paññānaṃ saṅkhārupekkhataṃ icchantena pana‘‘ paññā’’ ti ca‘‘ saṅkhārupekkhāsū’’ ti ca bahuvacanaṃ kataṃ, avatthābhedena bhinnassāpi ekattā‘‘ ñāṇan’’ ti ekavacanaṃ katanti veditabbaṃ. "
563437,120,126,110,111,1,8,1,Vuttañca–
563438,120,126,112,142,1,108,15,"‘‘ yā ca muñcitukamyatā yā ca paṭisaṅkhānupassanā yā ca saṅkhārupekkhā, ime dhammā ekaṭṭhā, byañjanameva nānan’’ ti( paṭi. ma.1.227). "
563439,120,126,143,156,1,102,9,Keci pana‘‘ saṅkhārupekkhāsūti bahuvacanaṃ samathavipassanāvasena saṅkhārupekkhānaṃ bahuttā’’ tipi vadanti. 
563440,120,126,157,162,1,48,4,Saṅkhārupekkhāsūti ca kiriyāpekkhanti veditabbaṃ. 
563441,120,126,163,184,1,230,20,"Avatthābhedena pana tena nibbidāñāṇena nibbindantassa ukkaṇṭhantassa sabbabhavayonigativiññāṇaṭṭhitisattāvāsagatesu sabhedakesu saṅkhāresu cittaṃ na sajjati na laggati na bajjhati, sabbasaṅkhāragataṃ muñcitukāmaṃ chaḍḍetukāmaṃ hoti. "
563442,120,127,2,47,1,379,35,"Atha vā yathā jālabbhantaragato maccho, sappamukhagato maṇḍūko, pañjarapakkhitto vanakukkuṭo, daḷhapāsavasaṃgato migo, ahituṇḍikahatthagato sappo, mahāpaṅkapakkhando kuñjaro, supaṇṇamukhagato nāgarājā, rāhumukhapaviṭṭho cando, sapattaparikkhitto purisotievamādayo tato tato muccitukāmā nissaritukāmāva honti, evaṃ tassa yogino cittaṃ sabbasmā saṅkhāragatā muccitukāmaṃ nissaritukāmaṃ hoti. "
563443,120,127,48,59,1,63,7,Evañhi vuccamāne‘‘ muccitukāmassa muccitukamyatā’’ ti pāṭho yujjati. 
563444,120,127,60,85,1,122,15,"Evañca sati‘‘ uppādaṃ muñcitukamyatā’’ tiādīsu‘‘ uppādā muccitukamyatā’’ tiādi vattabbaṃ hoti, tasmā purimo eva attho sundarataro. "
563445,120,127,86,93,1,101,7,Athassa sabbasaṅkhāresu vigatālayassa sabbasaṅkhāragataṃ muñcitukāmassa muñcitukamyatāñāṇaṃ uppajjati. 
563446,120,127,94,110,1,192,16,So evaṃ sabbabhavayonigativiññāṇaṭṭhitisattāvāsagate sabhedake saṅkhāre muñcitukāmo muñcanassa upāyasampādanatthaṃ puna te eva saṅkhāre paṭisaṅkhānupassanāñāṇena tilakkhaṇaṃ āropetvā vipassati. 
563447,120,127,111,129,1,179,16,"Evañhi vipassato cassa aniccavasena nimittaṃ paṭisaṅkhāñāṇaṃ uppajjati, dukkhavasena pavattaṃ paṭisaṅkhāñāṇaṃ uppajjati, anattavasena nimittañca pavattañca paṭisaṅkhāñāṇaṃ uppajjati. "
563448,120,127,130,177,1,265,34,"So paṭisaṅkhānupassanāñāṇena‘‘ sabbe saṅkhārā suññā’’ ti disvā tilakkhaṇaṃ āropetvā saṅkhāre pariggaṇhanto bhayañca nandiñca vippahāya bhariyāya dosaṃ disvā vissaṭṭhabhariyo viya puriso tassā bhariyāya saṅkhāresu udāsīno hoti majjhatto,‘‘ ahan’’ ti vā‘‘ maman’’ ti vā na gaṇhāti. "
563449,120,127,178,191,1,101,13,Tassa evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato tīsu bhavesu cittaṃ patilīyati paṭikuṭati paṭivattati na sampasāriyati. 
563450,120,127,192,204,1,110,11,Seyyathāpi nāma padumapalāse īsakaṃ poṇe udakaphusitāni patilīyanti paṭikuṭanti paṭivattanti na sampasāriyanti. 
563451,120,127,205,233,1,221,26,"Seyyathāpi vā pana kukkuṭapattaṃ vā nhārudaddulaṃ vā aggimhi pakkhittaṃ patilīyati paṭikuṭati paṭivattati na sampasāriyati, evaṃ tassa tīsu bhavesu cittaṃ patilīyati paṭikuṭati paṭivattati na sampasāriyati, upekkhā saṇṭhāti. "
563452,120,127,234,238,1,42,4,Evamassa saṅkhārupekkhāñāṇaṃ uppannaṃ hoti. 
563453,120,127,239,251,1,132,12,Iminā saṅkhārupekkhāñāṇena saddhiṃ upari gotrabhuñāṇassa sādhakaṃ anulomañāṇaṃ pubbāparañāṇehi avuttampi vuttameva hotīti veditabbaṃ. 
563454,120,127,252,254,1,18,2,Vuttañhi bhagavatā–
563455,120,128,2,66,1,365,39,"‘ ‘ So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato samanupassanto anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato bhavissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati, anulomikāya khantiyā asamannāgato sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati, sammattaniyāmaṃ anokkamamāno sotāpattiphalaṃ vā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ vā anāgāmiphalaṃ vā arahattaphalaṃ vā sacchikarissatīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjatī’’ tiādi( a. ni.6.98; paṭi. ma.3.36). "
563456,120,129,2,4,1,25,2,Vuttañca dhammasenāpatinā–
563457,120,130,2,8,1,43,5,‘ ‘ Katihākārehi anulomikaṃ khantiṃ paṭilabhati? 
563458,120,130,9,12,1,37,3,Katihākārehi sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamati? 
563459,120,130,13,36,1,102,10,"Cattālīsāya ākārehi anulomikaṃ khantiṃ paṭilabhati, cattālīsāya ākārehi sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamatī’’ tiādi( paṭi. ma.3.37). "
563460,120,131,2,6,1,31,4,Paṭṭhāne cetaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā–
563461,120,132,2,8,1,46,5,‘ ‘ Anulomaṃ gotrabhussa anantarapaccayena paccayo. 
563462,120,132,9,25,1,51,5,Anulomaṃ vodānassa anantarapaccayena paccayo’’ tiādi( paṭṭhā.1.1.417). 
563463,120,133,2,25,1,204,19,"Tassa hi taṃ saṅkhārupekkhāñāṇaṃ āsevantassa bhāventassa bahulīkarontassa adhimokkhasaddhā balavatarā hoti, vīriyaṃ supaggahitaṃ, sati sūpaṭṭhitā, cittaṃ susamāhitaṃ, saṅkhārupekkhāñāṇaṃ tikkhataraṃ pavattati. "
563464,120,133,26,56,1,126,18,Tassa idāni maggo uppajjissatīti saṅkhārupekkhāya saṅkhāre‘‘ aniccā’’ ti vā‘‘ dukkhā’’ ti vā‘‘ anattā’’ ti vā sammasitvā bhavaṅgaṃ otarati. 
563465,120,133,57,86,1,142,17,Bhavaṅgānantaraṃ saṅkhārupekkhāya katanayeneva saṅkhāre‘‘ aniccā’’ ti vā‘‘ dukkhā’’ ti vā‘‘ anattā’’ ti vā ārammaṇaṃ kurumānaṃ uppajjati manodvārāvajjanaṃ. 
563466,120,133,87,98,1,90,11,Tadanantaraṃ tatheva saṅkhāre ārammaṇaṃ katvā dve tīṇi cattāri vā javanacittāni uppajjanti. 
563467,120,133,99,103,1,33,3,Taṃsampayuttaṃ ñāṇaṃ anulomañāṇaṃ. 
563468,120,133,104,117,1,136,12,"Tañhi purimānañca aṭṭhannaṃ vipassanāñāṇānaṃ tathakiccatāya anulometi, upari ca pattabbānaṃ sattatiṃsāya bodhipakkhiyadhammānaṃ anulometi. "
563469,120,133,118,147,1,216,24,"Yathā hi dhammiko rājā vinicchayaṭṭhāne nisinno aṭṭhannaṃ vohārikamahāmattānaṃ vinicchayaṃ sutvā agatigamanaṃ pahāya majjhatto hutvā‘‘ evaṃ hotū’’ ti anumodamāno tesañca vinicchayassa anulometi, porāṇassa ca rājadhammassa. "
563470,120,133,148,195,1,391,38,"Tattha rājā viya anulomañāṇaṃ, aṭṭha vohārikamahāmattā viya aṭṭha vipassanāñāṇāni, porāṇarājadhammo viya sattatiṃsa bodhipakkhiyadhammā, yathā rājā‘‘ evaṃ hotū’’ ti anumodamāno vohārikānañca vinicchayassa rājadhammassa ca anulometi, evamidaṃ aniccādivasena saṅkhāre ārabbha uppajjamānānaṃ aṭṭhannañca vipassanāñāṇānaṃ tathakiccatāya anulometi, upari ca pattabbānaṃ sattatiṃsāya bodhipakkhiyadhammānaṃ. "
563471,120,133,196,199,1,28,3,Tasmā anulomañāṇanti vuccati. 
563472,120,134,2,15,1,83,8,10. Bahiddhā vuṭṭhānavivaṭṭane paññā gotrabhuñāṇan ti ettha {bahiddhā}ti saṅkhāranimittaṃ. 
563473,120,134,16,22,1,68,6,Tañhi ajjhattacittasantāne akusalakkhandhe upādāya bahiddhāti vuttaṃ. 
563474,120,134,23,44,1,186,18,"Tasmā bahiddhā saṅkhāranimittamhā vuṭṭhāti vigataṃ hutvā uddhaṃ tiṭṭhatīti vuṭṭhānaṃ, vivaṭṭati parāvaṭṭati parammukhaṃ hotīti vivaṭṭanaṃ, vuṭṭhānañca taṃ vivaṭṭanañcāti vuṭṭhānavivaṭṭanaṃ. "
563475,120,134,45,46,1,8,1,Tenevāha–
563476,120,135,2,28,1,127,15,"‘ ‘ Gotrabhuñāṇaṃ samudayassa asamucchindanato pavattā na vuṭṭhāti, nibbānārammaṇato pana nimittā vuṭṭhātīti ekato vuṭṭhānaṃ hotī’’ ti( visuddhi.2.827). "
563477,120,136,2,5,1,56,3,Puthujjanagottābhibhavanato ariyagottabhāvanato gotrabhu. 
563478,120,136,6,40,1,496,33,Idañhi anulomañāṇehi padumapalāsato udakamiva sabbasaṅkhārato patilīyamānacittassa anulomañāṇassa āsevanante animittaṃ nibbānaṃ ārammaṇaṃ kurumānaṃ puthujjanagottaṃ puthujjanasaṅkhaṃ puthujjanabhūmiṃ atikkamamānaṃ ariyagottaṃ ariyasaṅkhaṃ ariyabhūmiṃ okkamamānaṃ nibbānārammaṇe paṭhamāvattanapaṭhamābhogapaṭhamasamannāhārabhūtaṃ maggassa anantarasamanantarāsevanaupanissayanatthivigatavasena chahi ākārehi paccayabhāvaṃ sādhayamānaṃ sikhāppattaṃ vipassanāya muddhabhūtaṃ apunarāvattakaṃ uppajjati. 
563479,120,137,2,20,1,94,13,"11. Dubhato vuṭṭhānavivaṭṭane paññā magge ñāṇan ti ettha {dubhato}ti ubhato, dvayatoti vā vuttaṃ hoti. "
563480,120,137,21,36,1,175,15,Kilesānaṃ samucchindanato kilesehi ca tadanuvattakakkhandhehi ca nibbānārammaṇakaraṇato bahiddhā sabbasaṅkhāranimittehi ca vuṭṭhāti vivaṭṭatīti dubhato vuṭṭhānavivaṭṭane paññā. 
563481,120,137,37,38,1,8,1,Tenevāha–
563482,120,138,2,27,1,140,14,"‘ ‘ Cattāripi maggañāṇāni animittārammaṇattā nimittato vuṭṭhahanti, samudayassa samucchindanato pavattā vuṭṭhahantīti dubhato vuṭṭhānāni hontī’’ ti( visuddhi.2.827). "
