564028,120,266,42,44,1,25,2,Ayaṃ kathetukamyatāpucchā. 
564029,120,266,45,58,1,121,8,"Pañcavidhā hi pucchā– adiṭṭhajotanāpucchā, diṭṭhasaṃsandanāpucchā, vimaticchedanāpucchā, anumatipucchā, kathetukamyatāpucchāti. "
564030,120,266,59,62,1,19,3,Tāsaṃ idaṃ nānattaṃ– 
564031,120,267,2,38,1,216,23,"Katamā adiṭṭhajotanā pucchā?( Mahāni.150; cūḷani. puṇṇakamāṇavapucchāniddesa12) pakatiyā lakkhaṇaṃ aññātaṃ hoti adiṭṭhaṃ atulitaṃ atīritaṃ avibhūtaṃ avibhāvitaṃ, tassa ñāṇāya dassanāya tulanāya tīraṇāya vibhūtāya vibhāvanatthāya pañhaṃ pucchati, ayaṃ adiṭṭhajotanāpucchā. "
564032,120,268,2,36,1,193,21,"Katamā diṭṭhasaṃsandanā pucchā?( Mahāni.150; cūḷani. puṇṇakamāṇavapucchāniddesa12) pakatiyā lakkhaṇaṃ ñātaṃ hoti diṭṭhaṃ tulitaṃ tīritaṃ vibhūtaṃ vibhāvitaṃ, so aññehi paṇḍitehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanatthāya pañhaṃ pucchati, ayaṃ diṭṭhasaṃsandanāpucchā. "
564033,120,269,2,40,1,137,20,"Katamā vimaticchedanā pucchā?( Mahāni.150; cūḷani. puṇṇakamāṇavapucchāniddesa12) pakatiyā saṃsayapakkhando hoti vimatipakkhando dveḷhakajāto‘‘ evaṃ nu kho, nanu kho, kiṃ nu kho, kathaṃ nu kho’’ ti? "
564034,120,269,41,48,1,65,6,"So vimaticchedanatthāya pañhaṃ pucchati, ayaṃ vimaticchedanāpucchā. "
