566457,120,730,101,105,1,40,4,Abhijjhādomanassanti ca samāsetvā vuttaṃ. 
566458,120,730,106,111,1,54,5,Saṃyuttaṅguttarapāṭhantaresu pana visuṃ katvā paṭhanti. 
566459,120,730,112,126,1,101,12,"Sā pana abhijjhāyanti patthayanti etāya, sayaṃ vā abhijjhāyati, abhijjhāyanamattameva vā esāti abhijjhā. "
566460,120,730,127,143,1,181,14,"Yasmā panettha abhijjhāgahaṇena kāmacchando, domanassagahaṇena byāpādo saṅgahaṃ gacchati, tasmā nīvaraṇapariyāpannabalavadhammadvayadassanena nīvaraṇappahānaṃ vuttaṃ hotīti veditabbaṃ. "
566461,120,731,2,36,1,346,27,"Visesena panettha abhijjhāvinayena kāyasampattimūlakassa anurodhassa, domanassavinayena kāyavipattimūlakassa virodhassa, abhijjhāvinayena ca kāye abhiratiyā, domanassavinayena kāyabhāvanāya anabhiratiyā, abhijjhāvinayena kāye abhūtānaṃ subhasukhabhāvādīnaṃ pakkhepassa, domanassavinayena kāye bhūtānaṃ asubhāsukhabhāvādīnaṃ apanayanassa pahānaṃ vuttaṃ. "
566462,120,731,37,44,1,60,7,Tena yogāvacarassa yogānubhāvo yogasamatthatā ca dīpitā hoti. 
566463,120,731,45,55,1,110,9,"Yogānubhāvo hi esa, yadayaṃ anurodhavirodhavippamutto aratiratisaho abhūtapakkhepabhūtāpanayanavirahito ca hoti. "
566464,120,731,56,65,1,105,9,Anurodhavirodhavippamutto cesa aratiratisaho abhūtaṃ apakkhipanto bhūtañca anapanento yogasamattho hotīti. 
566465,120,732,2,5,1,10,2,Aparo nayo–
566466,120,732,6,17,1,58,7,‘‘ kāye kāyānupassī’’ ti ettha anupassanāya kammaṭṭhānaṃ vuttaṃ.
566467,120,732,18,28,1,64,6,‘‘ Viharatī’’ ti ettha vuttavihārena kammaṭṭhānikassa kāyapariharaṇaṃ.
