566499,120,739,103,108,1,33,5,Evaṃ tāva desanā puggale tiṭṭhati. 
566500,120,739,109,124,1,97,11,Kāye pana‘‘ subhan’’ ti vipallāsappahānā kāyapariggāhikā sati maggena samijjhatīti kāyānupassanā nāma. 
