566508,120,740,20,37,1,172,16,"Yasmā ca niyamattho, tasmā paṭhamajjhānaṃ upasampajja viharaṇasamaye avijjamānānampi kāmānaṃ tassa paṭhamajjhānassa paṭipakkhabhāvaṃ kāmapariccāgeneva cassa adhigamaṃ dīpeti. "
566509,120,740,38,39,1,6,1,Kathaṃ?
566510,120,740,40,78,1,239,29,"‘‘ Vivicceva kāmehī’’ ti evañhi niyame kayiramāne idaṃ paññāyati– nūnimassa jhānassa kāmā paṭipakkhabhūtā, yesu sati idaṃ na pavattati, andhakāre sati padīpobhāso viya, tesaṃ pariccāgeneva cassa adhigamo hoti orimatīrapariccāgena pārimatīrassa viya. "
566511,120,740,79,82,1,22,3,Tasmā niyamaṃ karotīti. 
566512,120,741,2,20,1,123,15,"Tattha siyā, kasmā panesa pubbapadeyeva vutto, na uttarapade, kiṃ akusalehi dhammehi aviviccāpi jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyāti? "
566513,120,741,21,26,1,30,5,Na kho panetaṃ evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. 
566514,120,741,27,32,1,37,5,Taṃnissaraṇato hi pubbapade esa vutto. 
566515,120,741,33,41,1,85,8,Kāmadhātusamatikkamanato hi kāmarāgapaṭipakkhato ca idaṃ jhānaṃ kāmānameva nissaraṇaṃ. 
566516,120,741,42,43,1,7,1,Yathāha–
566517,120,741,44,59,1,44,5,‘‘ kāmānametaṃ nissaraṇaṃ yadidaṃ nekkhamman’’ ti ( itivu.72). 
566518,120,741,60,101,1,112,16,"Uttarapadepi pana yathā‘‘ idheva, bhikkhave, samaṇo, idha dutiyo samaṇo’’ ti( ma. ni.1.139; a. ni.4.241) ettha evakāro ānetvā vuccati, evaṃ vattabbo. "
566519,120,741,102,114,1,100,12,Na hi sakkā ito aññehipi nīvaraṇasaṅkhātehi akusalehi dhammehi avivicca jhānaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ. 
566520,120,741,115,131,1,85,11,Tasmā‘‘ vivicceva kāmehi vivicceva akusalehi dhammehī’’ ti evaṃ padadvayepi esa daṭṭhabbo. 
566521,120,741,132,151,1,322,17,"Padadvayepi ca kiñcāpi viviccāti iminā sādhāraṇavacanena tadaṅgavikkhambhanasamucchedapaṭippassaddhinissaraṇavivekā cittakāyaupadhivivekā ca saṅgahaṃ gacchanti, tathāpi pubbabhāge kāyavivekacittavivekavikkhambhanavivekā daṭṭhabbā, lokuttaramaggakkhaṇe kāyavivekacittavivekasamucchedavivekapaṭippassaddhivivekanissaraṇavivekā. "
566522,120,742,2,72,1,279,41,"Kāmehīti iminā pana padena ye ca mahāniddese‘‘ katame vatthukāmā manāpikā rūpā’’ tiādinā( mahāni.1) nayena vatthukāmā vuttā, ye ca tattheva vibhaṅge ca‘‘ chando kāmo, rāgo kāmo, chandarāgo kāmo, saṅkappo kāmo, rāgo kāmo, saṅkapparāgo kāmo’’ ti( mahāni.1; vibha.564) evaṃ kilesakāmā vuttā, te sabbepi saṅgahitā icceva daṭṭhabbā. "
566523,120,742,73,81,1,71,8,Evañhi sati vivicceva kāmehīti vatthukāmehipi viviccevāti attho yujjati. 
566524,120,742,82,86,1,26,4,Tena kāyaviveko vutto hoti. 
566525,120,743,2,12,1,82,9,Vivicca akusalehi {dhammehī}ti kilesakāmehi sabbākusalehi vā viviccāti attho yujjati. 
566526,120,743,13,17,1,27,4,Tena cittaviveko vutto hoti. 
566527,120,743,18,31,1,142,12,"Purimena cettha vatthukāmehi vivekavacanato eva kāmasukhapariccāgo, dutiyena kilesakāmehi vivekavacanato nekkhammasukhapariggaho vibhāvito hoti. "
566528,120,743,32,41,1,114,8,"Evaṃ vatthukāmakilesakāmavivekavacanatoyeva ca etesaṃ paṭhamena saṃkilesavatthuppahānaṃ, dutiyena saṃkilesappahānaṃ. "
566529,120,743,42,48,1,58,5,"Paṭhamena lolabhāvassa hetupariccāgo, dutiyena bālabhāvassa. "
566530,120,743,49,58,1,77,8,"Paṭhamena ca payogasuddhi, dutiyena āsayaposanaṃ vibhāvitaṃ hotīti viññātabbaṃ. "
566531,120,743,59,66,1,57,7,Esa tāva nayo kāmehīti ettha vuttakāmesu vatthukāmapakkhe. 
566532,120,744,2,14,1,95,11,Kilesakāmapakkhe pana chandoti ca rāgoti ca evamādīhi anekabhedo kāmacchandova kāmoti adhippeto. 
566533,120,744,15,50,1,195,22,"So ca akusalapariyāpannopi samāno‘‘ tattha katame kāmā, chando kāmo’’ tiādinā( vibha.564) nayena vibhaṅge upari jhānaṅgapaṭipakkhato visuṃ vutto, kilesakāmattā vā purimapade vutto, akusalapariyāpannattā dutiyapade. "
566534,120,744,51,57,1,50,6,Anekabhedato cassa kāmatoti avatvā kāmehīti vuttaṃ. 
566535,120,744,58,86,1,180,17,"Aññesampi ca dhammānaṃ akusalabhāve vijjamāne‘‘ tattha katame akusalā dhammā, kāmacchando’’ tiādinā( vibha.564) nayena vibhaṅge upari jhānaṅgapaccanīkapaṭipakkhabhāvadassanato nīvaraṇāneva vuttāni. "
566536,120,744,87,98,1,104,10,"Nīvaraṇāni hi jhānaṅgapaccanīkāni, tesaṃ jhānaṅgāneva paṭipakkhāni viddhaṃsakāni vināsakānīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
566537,120,744,99,123,1,145,16,"Tathā hi‘‘ samādhi kāmacchandassa paṭipakkho, pīti byāpādassa, vitakko thinamiddhassa, sukhaṃ uddhaccakukkuccassa, vicāro vicikicchāyā’’ ti peṭake vuttaṃ. "
566538,120,745,2,15,1,80,9,Evamettha ‘‘ vivicceva kāmehī’’ ti iminā kāmacchandassa vikkhambhanaviveko vutto hoti.
566539,120,745,16,27,1,59,7,‘‘ Vivicca akusalehi dhammehī’’ ti iminā pañcannampi nīvaraṇānaṃ. 
566540,120,745,28,35,1,71,6,"Agahitaggahaṇena pana paṭhamena kāmacchandassa, dutiyena sesanīvaraṇānaṃ. "
566541,120,745,36,46,1,121,9,"Tathā paṭhamena tīsu akusalamūlesu pañcakāmaguṇabhedavisayassa lobhassa, dutiyena āghātavatthubhedādivisayānaṃ dosamohānaṃ. "
566542,120,745,47,56,1,157,8,"Oghādīsu vā dhammesu paṭhamena kāmoghakāmayogakāmāsavakāmupādānaabhijjhākāyagantha kāmarāgasaññojanānaṃ, dutiyena avasesaoghayogāsavaupādānaganthasaṃyojanānaṃ. "
566543,120,745,57,64,1,77,6,"Paṭhamena taṇhāya taṃsampayuttakānañca, dutiyena avijjāya taṃsampayuttakānañca. "
