567228,120,930,2,11,1,70,6,"{Musā}ti visaṃvādanapurekkhārassa atthabhañjako vacīpayogo, kāyapayogo vā. "
567229,120,930,12,17,1,87,5,Visaṃvādanādhippāyena panassa paravisaṃvādakakāyavacīpayogasamuṭṭhāpikā cetanā musāvādo. 
