567235,120,930,71,100,1,204,24,"Pabbajitānaṃ appakampi telaṃ vā sappiṃ vā labhitvā hasādhippāyena‘‘ ajja gāme telaṃ nadī maññe sandatī’’ ti pūraṇakathānayena pavatto appasāvajjo, adiṭṭhaṃyeva pana diṭṭhantiādinā nayena vadantānaṃ mahāsāvajjo. "
567236,120,930,101,115,1,96,10,"Tassa cattāro sambhārā– atathaṃ vatthu, visaṃvādanacittaṃ, tajjo vāyāmo, parassa tadatthavijānananti. "
567237,120,931,2,22,1,111,17,"Yāya vācāya yassa taṃ vācaṃ bhāsati, tassa hadaye attano piyabhāvaṃ, parassa ca suññabhāvaṃ karoti, sā pisuṇā vācā. "
567238,120,931,23,43,1,119,18,"Yāya pana attānampi parampi pharusaṃ karoti, yā vācā sayampi pharusā neva kaṇṇasukhā na hadayasukhā vā, ayaṃ pharusā vācā. "
