567243,120,932,15,26,1,78,9,"Sā yassa bhedaṃ karoti, tassa appaguṇatāya appasāvajjā, mahāguṇatāya mahāsāvajjā. "
567244,120,932,27,64,1,180,24,"Tassā cattāro sambhārā – bhinditabbo paro,‘‘ iti ime nānā bhavissantī’’ ti bhedapurekkhāratā vā‘‘ iti ahaṃ piyo bhavissāmi vissāsiko’’ ti piyakamyatā vā, tajjo vāyāmo, tassa tadatthavijānananti. "
567245,120,932,65,73,1,56,7,"Pare pana abhinne kammapathabhedo natthi, bhinneyeva hoti. "
