567449,120,973,125,128,1,29,3,Ettha kallasaddo kammaññattho. 
567450,120,973,129,161,1,422,30,"Tasmā kasiṇānulomato kasiṇapaṭilomato kasiṇānulomapaṭilomato jhānānulomato jhānapaṭilomato jhānānulomapaṭilomato jhānukkantikato kasiṇukkantikato jhānakasiṇukkantikato aṅgasaṅkantito ārammaṇasaṅkantito aṅgārammaṇasaṅkantito aṅgavavatthānato ārammaṇavavatthānatoti imehi cuddasahi ākārehi, aṅgārammaṇavavatthānatoti iminā saha pañcadasahi vā ākārehi cittaparidamanena samādhissa kammaññabhāvakaraṇe kusalabhāvoti vuttaṃ hoti. "
567451,120,974,2,18,1,162,15,Samādhissa {gocarakusalatā}ti samādhissa gocaresu kasiṇādīsu ārammaṇesu taṃ taṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjitukāmatāya yathāruci āvajjanakaraṇavasena tesu ārammaṇesu chekabhāvo. 
