567466,120,977,5,13,1,44,5,Navake {rūpāvacaro}ti‘‘ katame dhammā rūpāvacarā? 
567467,120,977,14,37,1,134,13,Heṭṭhato brahmapārisajjaṃ pariyantaṃ karitvā uparito akaniṭṭhe deve antokaritvā’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.1289) nayena vuttesu rūpāvacaradhammesu pariyāpanno. 
567468,120,977,38,49,1,84,9,"Tatrāyaṃ vacanattho– rūpakkhandhasaṅkhātaṃ rūpaṃ ettha avacarati, na kāmoti rūpāvacaro. "
567469,120,977,50,71,1,66,8,Rūpakkhandhopi hi rūpanti vuccati‘‘ rūpakkhandho rūpan’’ tiādīsu( yama.1. khandhayamaka.2) viya. 
567470,120,977,72,82,1,213,10,So pana brahmapārisajjabrahmapurohitamahābrahmānaṃ parittābhaappamāṇābhaābhassarānaṃ parittasubhaappamāṇasubhasubhakiṇhānaṃ asaññasattavehapphalānaṃ avihātappasudassasudassīakaniṭṭhānañca vasena soḷasavidho padeso. 
567471,120,977,83,100,1,102,12,"So rūpāvacarasaṅkhāto padeso uttarapadalopaṃ katvā‘‘ rūpan’’ ti vuccati, tasmiṃ rūpe avacaratīti rūpāvacaro. "
