567888,120,1043,49,84,1,242,25,"Ettāvatā tena‘‘ vayadhammameva uppajjati, uppannañca vayaṃ upetī’’ ti iminā ākārena samapaññāsa lakkhaṇāni paṭivijjhitvā ṭhitaṃ udayabbayānupassanā nāma paṭhamaṃ taruṇavipassanāñāṇaṃ adhigataṃ hoti, yassādhigamā‘‘ āraddhavipassako’’ ti saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
567889,120,1043,85,113,1,185,21,"Imasmiṃ ñāṇe ṭhitassa obhāsādayo dasa vipassanūpakkilesā uppajjanti, yesaṃ uppattiyā akusalo yogāvacaro tesu maggañāṇasaññī hutvā amaggameva‘‘ maggo’’ ti gaṇhāti, upakkilesajaṭājaṭito ca hoti. "
567890,120,1043,114,140,1,189,21,"Kusalo pana yogāvacaro tesu vipassanaṃ āropento upakkilesajaṭaṃ vijaṭetvā‘‘ ete dhammā na maggo, upakkilesavimuttaṃ pana vīthipaṭipannaṃ vipassanāñāṇaṃ maggo’’ ti maggañca amaggañca vavatthapeti. "
567891,120,1043,141,149,1,81,8,Tassevaṃ maggañca amaggañca ñatvā ṭhitaṃ ñāṇaṃ maggāmaggañāṇadassanavisuddhi nāma. 
567892,120,1044,2,11,1,62,9,Ettāvatā ca pana tena catunnaṃ saccānaṃ vavatthānaṃ kataṃ hoti. 
567893,120,1044,12,13,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
567894,120,1044,14,66,1,629,45,"Nāmarūpapariggahe sati paccayapariggahasambhavato dhammaṭṭhitiñāṇavacaneneva vuttena diṭṭhivisuddhisaṅkhātena nāmarūpavavatthāpanena dukkhasaccassa vavatthānaṃ kataṃ hoti, kaṅkhāvitaraṇavisuddhisaṅkhātena paccayapariggahaṇena samudayasaccassa vavatthānaṃ, udayabbayānupassanena ca khaṇato udayabbayadassanena dukkhasaccassa vavatthānaṃ kataṃ, paccayato udayadassanena samudayasaccassa vavatthānaṃ, paccayato vayadassanena nirodhasaccassa vavatthānaṃ, yañcassa udayabbayadassanaṃ, maggovāyaṃ lokikoti tatra sammohavighātato imissañca maggāmaggañāṇadassanavisuddhiyaṃ vipassato sammā maggassa avadhāraṇena maggasaccassa vavatthānaṃ kataṃ. "
567895,120,1044,67,76,1,68,9,Evaṃ lokiyena tāva ñāṇena catunnaṃ saccānaṃ vavatthānaṃ kataṃ hotīti. 
