567917,120,1048,101,105,1,20,3,"Virajjati, no rajjati. "
567918,120,1048,106,122,1,97,14,"So evaṃ virajjanto lokikeneva tāva ñāṇena rāgaṃ nirodheti, no samudeti, samudayaṃ na karotīti attho. "
567919,120,1048,123,139,1,103,14,"Atha vā so evaṃ viratto yathā diṭṭhaṃ rūpagataṃ, tathā adiṭṭhampi anvayañāṇavasena nirodheti, no samudeti. "
