568013,120,1073,11,21,1,80,9,Dukkhan ti bhayan ti sāmisan ti {saṅkhārā}ti uppādādimuñcanañāṇassa kāraṇavacanāni. 
568014,120,1073,22,37,1,133,13,"Evañca lakkhaṇato saṅkhārupekkhaṃ dassetvā idāni atthato dassetuṃ uppādo saṅkhārā, te saṅkhāre ajjhupekkhatīti {saṅkhārupekkhā}tiādimāha. "
568015,120,1073,38,72,1,317,32,"Tattha saṅkhāre {ajjhupekkhatī}ti tassa āraddhavipassakassa vipassanāñāṇena lakkhaṇattayassa diṭṭhattā lakkhaṇavicinane pahīnabyāpārassa āditte viya tayo bhave passato saṅkhāraggahaṇe majjhattassa taṃ vipassanāñāṇaṃ te saṅkhāre visesena ca ikkhati, gahaṇena vajjitañca hutvā ikkhati oloketīti saṅkhārupekkhā nāmāti attho. "
568016,120,1073,73,84,1,83,10,"Yathā loke visesena jayanto adhijayatīti, annena vajjito vasanto upavasatīti vuccati. "
