568234,120,1112,121,134,1,160,11,"Tiṇṇaṃ vimokkhāna {paccayā}ti tiṇṇaṃ lokuttaravimokkhānaṃ samathagotrabhu pakatūpanissayapaccayā honti, vipassanāgotrabhu anantarasamanantarūpanissayapaccayā honti. "
568235,120,1112,135,143,1,64,7,Paññā yassa {pariccitā}ti pubbabhāgapaññā yassa paricitā pariciṇṇā. 
568236,120,1112,144,157,1,111,11,"Kusalo vivaṭṭe {vuṭṭhāne}ti asammohavaseneva vivaṭṭasaṅkhāte gotrabhuñāṇe kusalo cheko, pubbabhāgañāṇena vā kusalo. "
568237,120,1112,158,168,1,83,9,Nānādiṭṭhīsu na {kampatī}ti samucchedena pahīnāsu nānappakārāsu diṭṭhīsu na vedhatīti. 
568238,120,1113,2,4,1,35,2,Gotrabhuñāṇaniddesavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
568239,120,1114,2,4,1,23,2,11 . Maggañāṇaniddesavaṇṇanā 
568240,120,1115,2,15,1,122,8,61. Maggañāṇaniddese micchādiṭṭhiyā {vuṭṭhātī}ti diṭṭhānusayappahānena samucchedavasena dvāsaṭṭhibhedato micchādiṭṭhito vuṭṭhāti. 
568241,120,1115,16,26,1,144,9,{Tadanuvattakakilesehī}ti micchādiṭṭhisampayogavasena ca micchādiṭṭhiupanissayena ca uppajjamānehi micchādiṭṭhianuvattamānehi nānāvidhehi kilesehi. 
568242,120,1115,27,31,1,41,4,Tena tadekaṭṭhakilesappahānaṃ vuttaṃ hoti. 
568243,120,1115,32,36,1,49,4,Duvidhañhi ekaṭṭhaṃ sahajekaṭṭhaṃ pahānekaṭṭhañca. 
568244,120,1115,37,50,1,82,12,"Tāya diṭṭhiyā saha ekasmiṃ citte, ekasmiṃ puggale vā yāva pahānā ṭhitāti tadekaṭṭhā. "
568245,120,1115,51,83,1,284,31,"Diṭṭhiyā hi pahīyamānāya diṭṭhisampayuttesu dvīsu asaṅkhārikacittesu tāya diṭṭhiyā sahajātā lobho moho uddhaccaṃ ahirikaṃ anottappanti ime kilesā, dvīsu sasaṅkhārikacittesu tāya diṭṭhiyā sahajātā lobho moho thinaṃ uddhaccaṃ ahirikaṃ anottappanti ime kilesā sahajekaṭṭhavasena pahīyanti. "
568246,120,1115,84,106,1,184,21,Diṭṭhikileseyeva pahīyamāne tena saha ekasmiṃ puggale ṭhitā apāyagamanīyā lobho doso moho māno vicikicchā thinaṃ uddhaccaṃ ahirikaṃ anottappanti ime kilesā pahānekaṭṭhavasena pahīyanti. 
568247,120,1115,107,131,1,240,21,"{Khandhehī}ti tadanuvattakeheva khandhehi, taṃ diṭṭhiṃ anuvattamānehi sahajekaṭṭhehi ca pahānekaṭṭhehi ca catūhi arūpakkhandhehi, taṃsamuṭṭhānarūpehi vā saha pañcahi khandhehi micchādiṭṭhiādikilesapaccayā anāgate uppajjitabbehi vipākakkhandhehi. "
568248,120,1115,132,139,1,90,6,Bahiddhā ca {sabbanimittehī}ti yathāvuttakilesakkhandhato bahibhūtehi sabbasaṅkhāranimittehi. 
568249,120,1115,140,156,1,178,14,"Micchāsaṅkappā {vuṭṭhātī}ti sotāpattimaggena pahātabbesu catūsu diṭṭhisampayuttesu, vicikicchāsahagate cāti pañcasu cittesu apāyagamanīyasesākusalacittesu ca micchāsaṅkappā vuṭṭhāti. "
568250,120,1116,2,11,1,93,7,Micchāvācāya {vuṭṭhātī}ti musāvādato ceva apāyagamanīyapisuṇapharusasamphappalāpehi ca vuṭṭhāti . 
568251,120,1116,12,17,1,66,4,Micchākammantā {vuṭṭhātī}ti pāṇātipātādinnādānamicchācārehi vuṭṭhāti. 
568252,120,1116,18,33,1,138,12,"Micchāājīvā {vuṭṭhātī}ti kuhanā lapanā nemittikatā nippesikatā lābhenalābhaṃnijigīsanatā, ājīvahetukehi vā sattahipi kāyavacīkammehi vuṭṭhāti. "
568253,120,1116,34,39,1,95,5,Micchāvāyāmamicchāsatimicchāsamādhīhi vuṭṭhānaṃ micchāsaṅkappavuṭṭhāne vuttanayeneva veditabbaṃ. 
568254,120,1116,40,47,1,78,6,{Micchāsatī}ti ca satiyā paṭipakkhākārena uppajjamānā akusalacittuppādamattameva. 
568255,120,1116,48,65,1,130,12,"Uparimaggattaye‘‘ dassanaṭṭhena sammādiṭṭhī’’ tiādīni aṭṭha maggaṅgāni yathā paṭhamajjhānike paṭhamamagge labbhanti, tatheva labbhanti. "
568256,120,1116,66,72,1,68,6,Tattha paṭhamamagge sammādiṭṭhi micchādiṭṭhiṃ pajahatīti sammādiṭṭhi. 
568257,120,1116,73,77,1,66,4,Sammāsaṅkappādayopi micchāsaṅkappādīnaṃ pajahanaṭṭheneva veditabbā. 
568258,120,1116,78,89,1,110,11,Evaṃ sante paṭhamamaggeneva dvāsaṭṭhiyā diṭṭhigatānaṃ pahīnattā uparimaggattayena pahātabbā diṭṭhi nāma natthi. 
568259,120,1117,2,7,1,40,5,Tattha sammādiṭṭhīti nāmaṃ kathaṃ hotīti? 
568260,120,1117,8,32,1,120,21,"Yathā visaṃ atthi vā hotu mā vā, agado agadotveva vuccati, evaṃ micchādiṭṭhi atthi vā hotu mā vā, ayaṃ sammādiṭṭhi eva nāma. "
568261,120,1117,33,47,1,112,12,"Yadi evaṃ nāmamattamevetaṃ hoti, uparimaggattaye pana sammādiṭṭhiyā kiccābhāvo āpajjati, maggaṅgāni na paripūrenti. "
568262,120,1117,48,55,1,64,6,"Tasmā sammādiṭṭhi sakiccakā kātabbā, maggaṅgāni paripūretabbānīti. "
568263,120,1117,56,61,1,57,5,Sakiccakā cettha sammādiṭṭhi yathālābhaniyamena dīpetabbā. 
568264,120,1117,62,77,1,100,13,"Uparimaggattayavajjho hi eko māno atthi, so diṭṭhiṭṭhāne tiṭṭhati, sā taṃ mānaṃ pajahatīti sammādiṭṭhi. "
568265,120,1117,78,83,1,55,4,Sotāpattimaggasmiñhi sammādiṭṭhi micchādiṭṭhiṃ pajahati. 
568266,120,1117,84,94,1,83,9,"Sotāpannassa pana sakadāgāmimaggavajjho māno atthi, taṃ mānaṃ pajahatīti sammādiṭṭhi. "
568267,120,1117,95,123,1,224,21,"Tasseva sattaakusalacittasahajāto saṅkappo atthi, teheva cittehi vācaṅgacopanaṃ atthi, kāyaṅgacopanaṃ atthi, paccayaparibhogo atthi, sahajātavāyāmo atthi, assatiyabhāvo atthi, sahajātacittekaggatā atthi, ete micchāsaṅkappādayo nāma. "
568268,120,1117,124,130,1,78,6,Sakadāgāmimagge sammāsaṅkappādayo tesaṃ pahānena sammāsaṅkappādayoti veditabbā. 
568269,120,1117,131,137,1,49,5,Evaṃ sakadāgāmimagge aṭṭhaṅgāni sakiccakāni honti. 
568270,120,1117,138,146,1,68,7,"Sakadāgāmissa anāgāmimaggavajjho māno atthi, so diṭṭhiṭṭhāne tiṭṭhati. "
568271,120,1117,147,153,1,51,6,Tasseva sattahi cittehi sahajātā saṅkappādayo atthi. 
568272,120,1117,154,161,1,67,7,Tesaṃ pahānena anāgāmimagge aṭṭhannaṃ aṅgānaṃ sakiccakatā veditabbā. 
568273,120,1117,162,170,1,66,7,"Anāgāmissa arahattamaggavajjho māno atthi, so diṭṭhiṭṭhāne tiṭṭhati. "
568274,120,1117,171,180,1,66,8,"Yāni panassa pañca akusalacittāni, tehi sahajātā saṅkappādayo atthi. "
568275,120,1117,181,188,1,68,7,Tesaṃ pahānena arahattamagge aṭṭhannaṃ aṅgānaṃ sakiccakatā veditabbā. 
568276,120,1118,2,8,1,65,5,{Oḷārikā}ti kāyavacīdvāre vītikkamassa paccayabhāvena thūlabhūtamhā. 
568277,120,1118,9,13,1,49,3,{Kāmarāgasaññojanā}ti methunarāgasaṅkhātā saññojanā. 
568278,120,1118,14,21,1,48,6,So hi kāmabhave saññojetīti saññojananti vuccati. 
568279,120,1118,22,25,1,35,2,{Paṭighasaññojanā}ti byāpādasaññojanā. 
568280,120,1118,26,32,1,47,6,So hi ārammaṇe paṭihaññatīti paṭighanti vuccati. 
568281,120,1118,33,39,1,49,6,Te eva thāmagataṭṭhena santāne anusentīti anusayā. 
568282,120,1118,40,46,1,43,4,"{Aṇusahagatā}ti aṇubhūtā, sukhumabhūtāti attho. "
568283,120,1118,47,51,1,31,4,Tabbhāve hi ettha sahagatasaddo. 
568284,120,1118,52,62,1,100,10,Sakadāgāmissa hi kāmarāgabyāpādā dvīhi kāraṇehi aṇubhūtā adhiccuppattiyā ca pariyuṭṭhānamandatāya ca. 
568285,120,1118,63,75,1,88,11,"Tassa hi bālaputhujjanassa viya kilesā abhiṇhaṃ na uppajjanti, kadāci karahaci uppajjanti. "
568286,120,1118,76,102,1,203,24,"Uppajjamānā ca bālaputhujjanassa viya maddantā pharantā chādentā andhaandhaṃ karontā na uppajjanti, dvīhi pana maggehi pahīnattā mandamandā tanukākārā hutvā uppajjanti, vītikkamaṃ pāpetuṃ samatthā na honti. "
568287,120,1118,103,111,1,71,7,Evaṃ tanubhūtā anāgāmimaggena pahīyanti {rūparāgā}ti rūpabhave chandarāgā. 
