568293,120,1119,2,11,1,58,5,62. Idāni maggañāṇasaṃvaṇṇanaṃ karonto ajātaṃ {jhāpetī}tiādimāha. 
568294,120,1119,12,45,1,239,29,"Tattha ca ajātaṃ jhāpeti jātena, jhānaṃ tena {pavuccatī}ti attano santāne pātubhūtena tena tena lokuttarajjhānena taṃsamaṅgīpuggalo ajātameva taṃ taṃ kilesaṃ jhāpeti dahati samucchindati, tena kāraṇena taṃ lokuttaraṃ jhānanti pavuccatīti attho. "
568295,120,1119,46,65,1,180,17,Jhānavimokkhe {kusalatā}ti tasmiṃ ariyamaggasampayutte vitakkādike jhāne ca vimokkhasaṅkhāte ariyamagge ca asammohavasena kusalatāya paṭhamamaggeneva pahīnāsu nānādiṭṭhīsu na kampati. 
568296,120,1119,66,71,1,64,5,Jhānaṃ nāma duvidhaṃ ārammaṇūpanijjhānañca lakkhaṇūpanijjhānañca. 
568297,120,1119,72,84,1,187,10,"Lokiyapaṭhamajjhānādikaṃ kasiṇādiārammaṇūpanijjhānaṭṭhena jhānaṃ, vipassanāsaṅkhārānaṃ sabhāvasāmaññalakkhaṇūpanijjhānaṭṭhena jhānaṃ, lokuttaraṃ nibbāne tathalakkhaṇūpanijjhānaṭṭhena jhānaṃ. "
568298,120,1119,85,95,1,115,10,Idha pana gotrabhunāpi sādhāraṇaṃ lakkhaṇūpanijjhānaṭṭhaṃ anāmasitvā asādhāraṇena kilesajhāpanaṭṭhena jhānaṃ vuttaṃ. 
568299,120,1119,96,105,1,90,9,Vimokkhaṭṭho panettha nibbānārammaṇe suṭṭhu adhimuccanaṭṭho kilesehi ca suṭṭhu muccanaṭṭho. 
568300,120,1120,2,17,1,140,14,Samādahitvā yathā ce {vipassatī}ti appanūpacārakhaṇikasamādhīnaṃ aññatarena samādhinā paṭhamaṃ cittasamādhānaṃ katvā pacchā yathā vipassati ca. 
568301,120,1120,18,22,1,44,4,Samuccayattho ce-saddo vipassanaṃ samuccinoti. 
568302,120,1120,23,38,1,108,13,"Vipassamāno tathā ce {samādahe}ti vipassanā nāmesā lūkhabhūtā nirassādā, samatho ca nāma siniddhabhūto saassādo. "
568303,120,1120,39,48,1,69,9,Tasmā tāya lūkhabhūtaṃ cittaṃ sinehetuṃ vipassamāno tathā ca samādahe. 
568304,120,1120,49,60,1,96,10,"Vipassamāno puna samādhiṃ pavisitvā cittasamādhānañca tatheva kareyya, yatheva vipassananti attho. "
568305,120,1120,61,65,1,36,4,Idha ce-saddo samādahanaṃ samuccinoti. 
568306,120,1120,66,76,1,73,8,"Ubhayatthāpi gāthābandhānuvattanena ce-kāro kato, attho pana ca-kārattho eva. "
568307,120,1120,77,108,1,239,27,"Vipassanā ca samatho tadā {ahū}ti yasmā samathavipassanānaṃ yuganaddhabhāve sati ariyamaggapātubhāvo hoti, tasmā ariyamaggajananasamatthattā yadā tadubhayasamāyogo hoti, tadā vipassanā ca samatho ca ahu, samathavipassanā bhūtā nāma hotīti attho. "
568308,120,1120,109,136,1,229,25,"Tā ca samathavipassanā ariyamaggābhimukhīkāle ca maggakkhaṇe ca samānabhāgā yuganaddhā vattare samāno samo bhāgo koṭṭhāso etesanti samānabhāgā, yuge naddhā viyāti yuganaddhā, aññamaññaṃ anativattanaṭṭhena samadhurā samabalāti attho. "
568309,120,1120,137,141,1,49,4,Vitthāro panassa yuganaddhakathāyaṃ āvibhavissati. 
568310,120,1121,2,9,1,42,6,"Dukkhā saṅkhārā sukho, nirodho iti dassanaṃ. "
568311,120,1121,10,34,1,166,20,"Dubhato vuṭṭhitā paññā, phasseti amataṃ padan ti dukkhā saṅkhārā, sukho nirodho nibbānanti paṭipannassa tato nibbānadassanaṃ ariyamaggañāṇaṃ dubhato vuṭṭhitā paññā nāma. "
568312,120,1121,35,47,1,83,11,"Sā eva ca paññā amataṃ padaṃ nibbānaṃ ārammaṇaphusanena phusati, paṭilabhatīti attho. "
568313,120,1121,48,70,1,187,20,"Nibbānañhi atappakaṭṭhena amatasadisanti amataṃ, nāssa mataṃ maraṇaṃ vayo atthītipi amataṃ, pubbabhāgato paṭṭhāya mahatā ussāhena mahatiyā paṭipadāya pajjati paṭipajjīyatīti padanti vuccati. "
568314,120,1122,2,11,1,90,7,"Vimokkhacariyaṃ {jānātī}ti vimokkhapavattiṃ asammohavasena jānāti, paccavekkhaṇavasena jānāti."
568315,120,1122,12,52,1,216,23,"‘‘ Dubhato vuṭṭhāno vimokkho, dubhato vuṭṭhānā cattāro vimokkhā, dubhato vuṭṭhānānaṃ anulomā cattāro vimokkhā, dubhato vuṭṭhānapaṭippassaddhi cattāro vimokkhā’’ ti hi upari vimokkhakathāyaṃyeva( paṭi. ma.1.209 ādayo) āgatā vimokkhacariyā veditabbā. "
568316,120,1122,53,57,1,29,4,Tesaṃ vitthāro tattheva āgato. 
568317,120,1122,58,66,1,67,7,{Nānattekattakovido}ti tesaṃ vimokkhānaṃ nānābhāve ekabhāve ca kusalo. 
568318,120,1122,67,85,1,169,15,"Dubhato vuṭṭhānavimokkhavasena hi tesaṃ ekattaṃ, catuariyamaggavasena nānattaṃ, ekekassāpi vā ariyamaggassa anupassanābhedena nānattaṃ, ariyamaggabhāvena ekattaṃ veditabbaṃ. "
568319,120,1122,86,98,1,106,11,Dvinnaṃ ñāṇānaṃ {kusalatā}ti dassanasaṅkhātassa ca bhāvanāsaṅkhātassa cāti imesaṃ dvinnaṃ ñāṇānaṃ kusalatāya. 
568320,120,1122,99,103,1,29,4,Dassanan ti hi sotāpattimaggo. 
568321,120,1122,104,110,1,48,6,So hi paṭhamaṃ nibbānadassanato dassananti vutto. 
568322,120,1122,111,166,1,331,41,"Gotrabhu pana kiñcāpi paṭhamataraṃ nibbānaṃ passati, yathā pana rañño santikaṃ kenacideva karaṇīyena āgato puriso dūratova rathikāya carantaṃ hatthikkhandhagataṃ rājānaṃ disvāpi‘‘ diṭṭho te rājā’’ ti puṭṭho disvā kattabbakiccassa akatattā‘‘ na passāmī’’ ti āha, evameva nibbānaṃ disvā kattabbassa kilesappahānassābhāvā na‘‘ dassanan’’ ti vuccati. "
568323,120,1122,167,172,1,44,5,Tañhi ñāṇaṃ maggassa āvajjanaṭṭhāne tiṭṭhati. 
