568326,120,1122,199,237,1,257,24,"Heṭṭhā pana bhāvanāmaggassa apariniṭṭhitattā‘‘ dvinnaṃ ñāṇānan’’ ti avatvā sotāpattisakadāgāmianāgāmimaggalābhino sandhāya‘‘ jhānavimokkhe kusalatā’’ ti vuttaṃ, arahattamaggalābhino pana bhāvanāmaggassa pariniṭṭhitattā‘‘ dvinnaṃ ñāṇānaṃ kusalatā’’ ti vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
