568328,120,1124,2,4,1,23,2,12 . Phalañāṇaniddesavaṇṇanā 
568329,120,1125,2,14,1,105,6,63. Phalañāṇaniddese {taṃpayogappaṭippassaddhattā}ti tassa ajjhattabahiddhā vuṭṭhānapayogassa paṭippassaddhattā. 
568330,120,1125,15,34,1,168,18,"Maggo hi sakakkhaṇe kilesappahānena ubhato vuṭṭhānapayogaṃ karoti nāma, phalakkhaṇe kilesānaṃ pahīnattā maggassa ubhato vuṭṭhānapayogo paṭippassaddho vūpasanto nāma hoti. "
568331,120,1125,35,58,1,192,19,"{Uppajjatī}ti maggānantaraṃ sakiṃ vā dvikkhattuṃ vā uppajjati, phalasamāpattikāle pana bahukkhattuṃ, nirodhā vuṭṭhahantassa dvikkhattuṃ uppajjati, sabbampi hi taṃ payogappaṭippassaddhattā uppajjati. "
568332,120,1125,59,66,1,62,7,Maggassetaṃ phalan ti phalaṃ apekkhitvā napuṃsakavacanaṃ kataṃ. 
568333,120,1125,67,71,1,74,4,Sakadāgāmimaggakkhaṇādīsupi ekekamaggaṅgavaseneva vuṭṭhānayojanā veditabbā. 
568334,120,1126,2,4,1,32,2,Phalañāṇaniddesavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
568335,120,1127,2,4,1,25,2,13 . Vimuttiñāṇaniddesavaṇṇanā 
568336,120,1128,2,21,1,132,13,"64. Vimuttiñāṇaniddese {sakkāyadiṭṭhī}ti vijjamānaṭṭhena sati khandhapañcakasaṅkhāte kāye, sayaṃ vā satī tasmiṃ kāye diṭṭhīti sakkāyadiṭṭhi. "
568337,120,1128,22,34,1,87,10,"{Vicikicchā}ti vigatā cikicchā, sabhāvaṃ vā vicinanto etāya kicchati kilamatīti vicikicchā. "
568338,120,1128,35,44,1,85,8,{Sīlabbataparāmāso}ti sīlena suddhi vatena suddhi sīlabbatena suddhīti gahitaabhiniveso. 
568339,120,1128,45,52,1,61,7,So hi sabhāvaṃ atikkamitvā parato āmasatīti sīlabbataparāmāso. 
568340,120,1128,53,69,1,201,16,Ubhinnaṃ samānepi diṭṭhibhāve takkañca parūpadesañca vinā pakatiyā eva sakkāyadiṭṭhigahaṇato pakatibhūtāya vīsativatthukāya sakkāyadiṭṭhiyā pahāneneva sabbadiṭṭhippahānadassanatthaṃ sakkāyadiṭṭhi vuttā. 
568341,120,1128,70,86,1,125,11,Sīlabbataparāmāso pana ‘‘ suddhipaṭipadaṃ paṭipajjāmā’’ ti paṭipannānaṃ paṭipadāya micchābhāvadassanatthaṃ visuṃ vuttoti veditabbo. 
