568353,120,1131,2,33,1,219,23,65. Paccavekkhaṇañāṇaniddese maggakkhaṇeyeva hetuṭṭhena paṭhamaṃ maggaṅgāni visuṃ visuṃ vatvā puna maggaṅgabhūte ca amaggaṅgabhūte ca dhamme‘‘ bujjhanaṭṭhena bodhī’’ ti laddhanāmassa ariyassa aṅgabhāvena bojjhaṅge visuṃ dassesi. 
568354,120,1131,34,40,1,102,5,"Satidhammavicayavīriyasamādhisambojjhaṅgā hi maggaṅgāneva, pītipassaddhiupekkhāsambojjhaṅgā amaggaṅgāni. "
568355,120,1131,41,50,1,76,9,Puna balavasena indriyavasena ca visuṃ niddiṭṭhesu saddhā eva amaggaṅgabhūtā. 
