568357,120,1131,60,72,1,162,11,Tattha upaṭṭhānaṭṭhena {satipaṭṭhānā}ti ekāva nibbānārammaṇā sati kāyavedanācittadhammesu subhasukhaniccaattasaññāpahānakiccasādhanavasena cattāro satipaṭṭhānā nāma. 
568358,120,1131,73,87,1,175,13,"Nibbānārammaṇaṃ ekameva vīriyaṃ uppannānuppannānaṃ akusalānaṃ pahānānuppattikiccassa, anuppannuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ uppādaṭṭhitikiccassa sādhanavasena cattāro sammappadhānā nāma. "
568359,120,1132,2,9,1,75,6,Tathaṭṭhena {saccā}ti dukkhabhāvādīsu avisaṃvādakaṭṭhena cattāri ariyasaccāni. 
568360,120,1132,10,33,1,145,17,"Etāneva cettha paṭivedhaṭṭhena tadā samudāgatāni,‘‘ amatogadhaṃ nibbānan’’ ti visuṃ vuttaṃ nibbānañca, sesā pana dhammā paṭilābhaṭṭhena tadā samudāgatā."
