568363,120,1132,100,104,1,31,4,Tathā paccavekkhaṇaṃ yujjati ca. 
568364,120,1132,105,110,1,49,4,{Samudayo}ti cettha taṃtaṃmaggavajjhoyeva veditabbo. 
