568948,120,1205,2,6,1,28,3,Tattha kā {nirodhasamāpattī}ti? 
568949,120,1205,7,12,1,61,5,Yā anupubbanirodhavasena cittacetasikānaṃ dhammānaṃ appavatti. 
568950,120,1206,2,10,1,40,6,"Ke taṃ samāpajjanti, ke na {samāpajjantī}ti? "
568951,120,1206,11,29,1,159,17,"Sabbepi puthujjanā sotāpannā sakadāgāmino sukkhavipassakā ca anāgāmī arahanto na samāpajjanti, aṭṭhasamāpattilābhino pana anāgāmino ca khīṇāsavā ca samāpajjanti. "
568952,120,1207,2,7,1,21,2,Kattha {samāpajjantī}ti? 
568953,120,1207,8,9,1,16,1,Pañcavokārabhave. 
568954,120,1207,10,11,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
568955,120,1207,12,13,1,27,1,Anupubbasamāpattisabbhāvato. 
568956,120,1207,14,25,1,93,10,"Catuvokārabhave pana paṭhamajjhānādīnaṃ uppattiyeva natthi, tasmā na sakkā tattha samāpajjituṃ. "
568957,120,1208,2,5,1,20,2,Kasmā {samāpajjantī}ti? 
568958,120,1208,6,24,1,126,14,Saṅkhārānaṃ pavattibhede ukkaṇṭhitvā diṭṭheva dhamme acittakā hutvā‘‘ nirodhaṃ nibbānaṃ patvā sukhaṃ viharissāmā’’ ti samāpajjanti. 
568959,120,1209,2,7,1,32,4,Kathaṃ cassā samāpajjanaṃ {hotī}ti? 
568960,120,1209,8,16,1,114,8,Samathavipassanāvasena ussakkitvā katapubbakiccassa nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ nirodhayato evamassā samāpajjanaṃ hoti. 
568961,120,1209,17,26,1,82,8,"Yo hi samathavaseneva ussakkati, so nevasaññānāsaññāyatanasamāpattiṃ patvā tiṭṭhati. "
568962,120,1209,27,35,1,64,7,"Yo vipassanāvaseneva ussakkati, so phalasamāpattiṃ patvā tiṭṭhati. "
568963,120,1209,36,48,1,105,11,"Yo pana ubhayavasena ussakkitvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ nirodheti, so taṃ samāpajjatīti ayamettha saṅkhepo. "
568964,120,1210,2,25,1,201,22,Ayaṃ pana vitthāro– idha bhikkhu nirodhaṃ samāpajjitukāmo katabhattakicco sudhotahatthapādo vivitte okāse supaññatte āsane nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. 
568965,120,1210,26,36,1,92,10,So paṭhamajjhānaṃ samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya tattha saṅkhāre aniccato dukkhato anattato vipassati. 
568966,120,1210,37,47,1,113,7,"Vipassanā panesā tividhā hoti– saṅkhārapariggaṇhanakavipassanā, phalasamāpattivipassanā, nirodhasamāpattivipassanāti. "
568967,120,1210,48,59,1,92,10,"Tattha saṅkhārapariggaṇhanakavipassanā mandā vā hotu tikkhā vā, maggassa padaṭṭhānaṃ hotiyeva. "
568968,120,1210,60,64,1,59,4,Phalasamāpattivipassanā tikkhāva vaṭṭati maggabhāvanāsadisā. 
568969,120,1210,65,70,1,59,5,Nirodhasamāpattivipassanā pana nātimandā nātitikkhā vaṭṭati. 
568970,120,1210,71,79,1,68,8,Tasmā esa nātimandāya nātitikkhāya vipassanāya te saṅkhāre vipassati. 
568971,120,1210,80,89,1,74,8,Tato dutiyajjhānaṃ samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya tattha saṅkhāre tatheva vipassati. 
568972,120,1210,90,103,1,100,11,Tato tatiyajjhānaṃ… pe… tato viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya tattha saṅkhāre tatheva vipassati. 
568973,120,1210,104,119,1,151,11,"Atha ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya catubbidhaṃ pubbakiccaṃ karoti– nānābaddhaavikopanaṃ, saṅghapaṭimānanaṃ, satthupakkosanaṃ, addhānaparicchedanti. "
568974,120,1211,2,41,1,276,34,"Tattha nānābaddhaavikopanan ti yaṃ iminā bhikkhunā saddhiṃ ekābaddhaṃ na hoti, nānābaddhaṃ hutvā ṭhitaṃ pattacīvaraṃ vā mañcapīṭhaṃ vā nivāsagehaṃ vā aññaṃ vā pana kiñci parikkhārajātaṃ, taṃ yathā na vikuppati, aggiudakavātacoraundūrādīnaṃ vasena na vinassati, evaṃ adhiṭṭhātabbaṃ. "
568975,120,1211,42,44,1,27,2,Tatridaṃ adhiṭṭhānavidhānaṃ–
568976,120,1211,45,73,1,140,19,"‘‘ idañcidañca imasmiṃ sattāhabbhantare mā agginā jhāyatu, mā udakena vuyhatu, mā vātena viddhaṃsatu, mā corehi harīyatu, mā undūrādīhi khajjatū’’ ti. "
568977,120,1211,74,88,1,97,13,"Evaṃ adhiṭṭhite taṃ sattāhaṃ tassa na koci parissayo hoti, anadhiṭṭhahato pana aggiādīhi vinassati. "
568978,120,1211,89,92,1,30,3,Idaṃ nānābaddhaavikopanaṃ nāma. 
568979,120,1211,93,110,1,125,15,"Yaṃ pana ekābaddhaṃ hoti nivāsanapārupanaṃ vā nisinnāsanaṃ vā, tattha visuṃ adhiṭṭhānakiccaṃ natthi, samāpattiyeva naṃ rakkhati. "
568980,120,1212,2,7,1,60,5,Saṅghapaṭimānanan ti bhikkhusaṅghassa paṭimānanaṃ udikkhanaṃ. 
568981,120,1212,8,17,1,63,8,"Yāva eso bhikkhu āgacchati, tāva saṅghakammassa akaraṇanti attho. "
568982,120,1212,18,28,1,78,9,"Ettha ca na paṭimānanaṃ etassa pubbakiccaṃ, paṭimānanāvajjanaṃ pana pubbakiccaṃ. "
568983,120,1212,29,32,1,23,3,Tasmā evaṃ āvajjitabbaṃ–
568984,120,1212,33,61,1,175,22,"‘‘ sace mayi sattāhaṃ nirodhaṃ samāpajjitvā nisinne saṅgho apalokanakammādīsu kiñcideva kammaṃ kattukāmo hoti, yāva maṃ koci bhikkhu āgantvā na pakkosati, tāvadeva vuṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti. "
568985,120,1212,62,69,1,50,7,Evaṃ katvā samāpanno hi tasmiṃ samaye vuṭṭhātiyeva. 
568986,120,1212,70,111,1,183,28,"Yo pana evaṃ na karoti, saṅgho ca sannipatitvā taṃ apassanto‘‘ asuko bhikkhu kuhin’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ nirodhaṃ samāpanno’’ ti vutte kañci bhikkhuṃ peseti‘‘ gaccha taṃ saṅghassa vacanena pakkosā’’ ti. "
568987,120,1212,112,129,1,103,13,Athassa tena bhikkhunā savanūpacāre ṭhatvā‘‘ saṅgho taṃ āvuso paṭimānetī’’ ti vuttamatteyeva vuṭṭhānaṃ hoti. 
568988,120,1212,130,136,1,32,5,Evaṃgarukā hi saṅghassa āṇā nāma. 
568989,120,1212,137,146,1,64,8,"Tasmā taṃ āvajjitvā yathā sayameva vuṭṭhāti, evaṃ samāpajjitabbaṃ. "
568990,120,1213,2,8,1,72,6,Satthupakkosanan ti idhāpi satthupakkosanāvajjanameva imassa pubbakiccaṃ. 
568991,120,1213,9,13,1,29,4,Tasmā tampi evaṃ āvajjitabbaṃ–
568992,120,1213,14,34,1,142,17,"‘‘ sace mayi sattāhaṃ nirodhaṃ samāpajjitvā nisinne satthā otiṇṇe vatthusmiṃ sikkhāpadaṃ vā paññapeti, tathārūpāya vā aṭṭhuppattiyā dhammaṃ deseti. "
568993,120,1213,35,47,1,60,9,"Yāva maṃ koci āgantvā na pakkosati, tāvadeva vuṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti. "
568994,120,1213,48,55,1,48,7,Evaṃ katvā nisinno hi tasmiṃ samaye vuṭṭhātiyeva. 
