569002,120,1214,29,44,1,129,13,"Sace hi sattāhabbhantare nirujjhanake āyusaṅkhāre anāvajjitvāva samāpajjati, tassa nirodhasamāpatti maraṇaṃ paṭibāhituṃ na sakkoti. "
569003,120,1214,45,56,1,101,10,"Antonirodhe maraṇassa natthitāya antarāva samāpattito vuṭṭhāti, tasmā etaṃ āvajjitvāva samāpajjitabbaṃ. "
569004,120,1214,57,65,1,67,7,"Avasesañhi anāvajjitumpi vaṭṭati, idaṃ pana āvajjitabbamevāti vuttaṃ. "
569005,120,1214,66,76,1,105,10,So evaṃ ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjitvā vuṭṭhāya imaṃ pubbakiccaṃ katvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjati. 
569006,120,1214,77,88,1,70,10,"Athekaṃ vā dve vā cittavāre atikkamitvā acittako hoti, nirodhaṃ phusati. "
