569017,120,1217,12,39,1,127,12,"‘‘ saññāvedayitanirodhasamāpattiyā vuṭṭhitassa kho, āvuso visākha, bhikkhuno vivekaninnaṃ cittaṃ hoti vivekapoṇaṃ vivekapabbhāran’’ ti( ma. ni.1.464). "
569018,120,1218,2,9,1,38,6,Matassa ca samāpannassa ca ko {viseso}ti? 
569019,120,1218,10,14,1,28,4,Ayampi attho sutte vuttoyeva. 
569020,120,1218,15,16,1,7,1,Yathāha–
