569052,120,1227,15,27,1,104,12,Na hi ekekassa vasena āyatanadhāturāsivajjehi sesehi aṭṭhahi rāsīhi visuṃ visuṃ sabbadhammo saṅgayhatīti. 
569053,120,1227,28,51,1,232,21,"Yasmā pana lokuttaradhammā hetusamucchedena samucchinditabbā na honti, tasmā sabbadhammasaddena saṅgahitāpi lokuttaradhammā samucchedavasena sambhavato idha na gahetabbā, hetusamucchedena samucchinditabbā eva tebhūmakadhammā gahetabbā. "
569054,120,1227,52,62,1,130,9,Sammā {samucchindatī}ti yathāyogaṃ vikkhambhanatadaṅgasamucchedapahānavasena pariyuṭṭhānaṃ anusayañca nirodhento sammā samucchindati. 
